# matplotlib.axes.Axes.set_rasterization_zorder

Axes.set_rasterization_zorder(z)[source]

    
Set the zorder threshold for rasterization for vector graphics output.

All artists with a zorder below the given value will be rasterized if they
support rasterization.

This setting is ignored for pixel-based output.

See also Rasterization for vector graphics.

Parameters

    
zfloat or None

    
The zorder below which artists are rasterized. If `None` rasterization based
on zorder is deactivated.
